am in the mapping, I mean I'm a big map obsessed
person particularly when it's like global

00:18:49.780 --> 00:18:55.540
health. It's so convenient and so user friendly.
So that is one of them. But then the other

00:18:55.540 --> 00:19:01.192
is I mean my alerts. I really could not keep
